data.meta_description: This is a complete list of events in Disney Magic Kingdoms in the order in which they happened. As mini events often repeat, the latest iteration of each mini event is displayed in bold. There has been a total of 538 mini events, out of which 340 occurred during a major event, while 198 occured...
